{"tid":2328358,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李偲嫣含羞少女照曝光曾做張國榮歌迷會會長 瘋狂追星為哥哥改名Lettie","createTime":"2020-12-16T13:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T13:18:44.000Z","uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e769ac94d4e345172d226e9e95082027e653fdf9","tid":2328358,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JrYiVMyLWpkIS7Y8tT2jMZS3LlY=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/52HMU3JFW5BXZHFY2R6LNE2HV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJrYiVMyLWpkIS7Y8tT2jMZS3LlY%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F52HMU3JFW5BXZHFY2R6LNE2HV4.jpg&h=50ba595f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李偲嫣疑患武肺猝死，終年56歲。身為死忠「藍絲」的正義聯盟創辦人李偲嫣，原名李艷青，在年輕時曾經瘋狂追星，是張國榮（Leslie、哥哥 )的忠實fans，甚至跟偶像改英文名為Lettie，不但加入了歌迷會，更擔任歌迷會的會長，可以出席活動跟哥哥接觸，甚至與其他歌迷一齊跟偶像合照，身為會長的她，可以站在哥哥身邊佔據有利位置，哥哥更搭着她的膊頭影相，這張合照更刊登在1989年出版的哥哥寫真集內。<br />\n<br />\n據哥哥當年歌迷會的fans張小姐所講，李偲嫣在80年代已擔任哥哥歌迷會會長，亦是哥哥第一代歌迷會會長。李偲嫣由哥哥剛出道，已是忠實fans，她做會長的任期內，約有百多名會員。張小姐說：「以我印象中，佢係一個辦事能力幾高嘅人，當時佢會自己整表格招募歌迷，而每次開歌迷聚會，佢都會親自打畀我哋，清楚交代所有細節，佢嗰時對我哋都幾nice，哥哥都好信任佢。」據知哥哥曾把李偲嫣介紹給一些資深傳媒人認識，打好關係，她亦經常不厭其煩地聯絡記者。<br />\n<br />\n她於2007年改名為李偲嫣，年輕時曾在無綫做臨時演員，之後去藝能唱片做幕後，90年代更開設娛樂公司，擔任鄺美雲、莫鎮賢、模特兒張沅薇的經理人，惟之後與藝人反面收場，鄺美雲和莫鎮賢都公開宣佈跟李偲嫣解約，有傳解約原因涉及錢銀瓜葛。<br />\n<br />\n李偲嫣曾有兩段婚姻，跟前夫育有一子，有消息指她的前夫是江湖人士。據知，當年她在娛樂圈時，曾跟前唱片公司高層Tommy拍拖，Tommy接受《蘋果》電話訪問表示：「我哋係舊同學，30幾年前喺呢行重遇之後拍拖，嗰時大家都係20幾歲，拍咗一段時間，分手後冇再聯絡，30幾年冇見面；今年好多朋友走咗，聽到佢離世，當然唔開心。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dZVHkz4KLjJtSgZmdtqKX08XEpI=/888x561/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JAIJ6GA3GJGJ5NCQITMFIVL6GM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdZVHkz4KLjJtSgZmdtqKX08XEpI%3D%2F888x561%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJAIJ6GA3GJGJ5NCQITMFIVL6GM.JPG&h=12025133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/o1B83Mbgk1gOnBvmRJYhVDInHAg=/502x749/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JV6KVP62IFA5ZJGRZCP3YWETT4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fo1B83Mbgk1gOnBvmRJYhVDInHAg%3D%2F502x749%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJV6KVP62IFA5ZJGRZCP3YWETT4.JPG&h=5a7e236c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ae8c9dd0394ff3e56517360d7924fc123272af0","tid":2328358,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:18:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201216/ULK33UV2PNGA3G6FXAP3RDMJNA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201216%2FULK33UV2PNGA3G6FXAP3RDMJNA%2F&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE14Xq8Qv2IeoILbHjSh09rgU%3D&h=65cc36a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201216%2FULK33UV2PNGA3G6FXAP3RDMJNA%2F&h=1653f9f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201216/ULK33UV2PNGA3G6FXAP3RDMJNA/</a>"}]}